# 题库设置 [POST /exercise/setting]

|参数|必选|类型|参数说明|
|---|---|---|---|
|token|Y|String|用户ID|
|identity|Y|Integer|0: 免费, 1: VIP|
|type|Y|Integer|0: 科目一, 1: 科目四, 2: 恢复驾照, 3: 资格证|
|subType|Y|Integer|0: 小车, 1: 货车, 2: 客车, 3: 摩托车, 4: 危险品, 5: 出租车, 6: 教练员|

+ Request (application/json)
  {
    "token": "qwkdpqwkdpjoj12312-0",
    "identity": 0,
    "type": 0,
    "subType": 3
  }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  {
      "c": 0,
      "m": "",
      "d": {

      }
  }

