# 提交答题结果 [POST /exercise/submit]

|参数|必选|类型|参数说明|
|---|---|---|---|
|token|Y|String|用户ID|
|result|Y|object[]|答题结果集合|

+ Request (application/json)
  {
    "token": "qwkdpqwkdpjoj12312-0",
    "result": [
      {
        "id": 1861, //题目ID
        "result": true //答题结果
      },{
        "id": 1231,
        "result": true
      },
    ]
  }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  {
      "c": 0,
      "m": "",
      "d": {

      }
  }
